yzed and the logic corrected where necessary to ensure it computes separability accurately.\\n\\n### Objectives\\n1. Review the logic of how `separability_matrix` handles nested CompoundModels.\\n2. Identify why the outputs and inputs are incorrectly marked as non-separable.\\n3. Make the necessary adjustments to ensure expected behavior is restored for nested models.\\n\\n### Suggested Areas to Review\\n- Look into the handling of attributes and connections between models in nested `CompoundModel` scenarios.\\n\\n### Deliverables\\n- Updated logic/code for `separability_matrix`.\\n- Ensure unit tests reflect the proposed changes.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_sPShtYiLsMQnOhVBn2G4X13d", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\": \"issues/separability_matrix_bug/testing_ticket.md\", \"content\": \"## Testing Ticket for Separability Matrix Bug Fix\\n\\n### Description\\nAfter implementing the fix for the `separability_matrix` of nested CompoundModels, proper testing must be executed to verify the accuracy of the changes.\\n\\n### Testing Strategy\\n1. Re-run the previously failing tests:\\n   - `test_separable[compound_model6-result6]`\\n   - `test_separable[compound_model9-result9]`\\n2. Create additional unit tests that specifically check the behavior of nested CompoundModels.\\n\\n### Expected Outcomes\\n- All tests related to separability of models should pass successfully after the fix.\\n- New tests should confirm correct behavior for various instances of nested CompoundModels.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}]}}], "created": 1777998164, "model": "gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "default", "system_fingerprint": "fp_b6580bbee1", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 666, "prompt_tokens": 1541, "total_tokens": 2207, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"a