2026-05-05 23:22:54,783 [INFO] autogen_core.events: {"type": "ToolCall", "tool_name": "board_write_file", "arguments": {"path": "issues/separability_matrix_bug/testing_ticket.md", "content": "## Testing Ticket for Separability Matrix Bug Fix\n\n### Description\nAfter implementing the fix for the `separability_matrix` of nested CompoundModels, proper testing must be executed to verify the accuracy of the changes.\n\n### Testing Strategy\n1. Re-run the previously failing tests:\n   - `test_separable[compound_model6-result6]`\n   - `test_separable[compound_model9-result9]`\n2. Create additional unit tests that specifically check the behavior of nested CompoundModels.\n\n### Expected Outcomes\n- All tests related to separability of models should pass successfully after the fix.\n- New tests should confirm correct behavior for various instances of nested CompoundModels."}, "result": "Successfully wrote to /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-129071/repeat_1/project_board/issues/separability_matrix_bug/testing_ticket.md", "agent_id": "ProjectManager_fc8f4551-28b7-412e-ac93-3dd44e594016/fc8f4551-28b7-412e-ac93-3dd44e594016"}
