n the previously failing tests:\\n   - `test_separable[compound_model6-result6]`\\n   - `test_separable[compound_model9-result9]`\\n2. Create additional unit tests that specifically check the behavior of nested CompoundModels.\\n\\n### Expected Outcomes\\n- All tests related to separability of models should pass successfully after the fix.\\n- New tests should confirm correct behavior for various instances of nested CompoundModels."}', name='board_write_file')], type='ToolCallRequestEvent'), ToolCallExecutionEvent(id='a7e68700-23eb-4fba-85ee-09883627e5cc', source='ProjectManager', models_usage=None, metadata={}, created_at=datetime.datetime(2026, 5, 5, 16, 22, 54, 783785, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), content=[FunctionExecutionResult(content='Successfully wrote to /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-129071/repeat_1/project_board/issues/separability_matrix_bug/diagnosis_ticket.md', name='board_write_file', call_id='call_gKd7632M0iFizS7XmqwCwIWy', is_error=False), FunctionExecutionResult(content='Successfully wrote to /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-129071/repeat_1/project_board/issues/separability_matrix_bug/implementation_ticket.md', name='board_write_file', call_id='call_WUszGFPhQKfMLT3iikUIQyrk', is_error=False), FunctionExecutionResult(content='Successfully wrote to /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-129071/repeat_1/project_board/issues/separability_matrix_bug/testing_ticket.md', name='board_write_file', call_id='call_sPShtYiLsMQnOhVBn2G4X13d', is_error=False)], type='ToolCallExecutionEvent')]), 'name': 'ProjectManager'}
