omes\\\\n- All tests related to separability of models should pass successfully after the fix.\\\\n- New tests should confirm correct behavior for various instances of nested CompoundModels.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\"}],\"results\":[{\"content\":\"Successfully wrote to /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-129071/repeat_1/project_board/issues/separability_matrix_bug/diagnosis_ticket.md\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_gKd7632M0iFizS7XmqwCwIWy\",\"is_error\":false},{\"content\":\"Successfully wrote to /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-129071/repeat_1/project_board/issues/separability_matrix_bug/implementation_ticket.md\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_WUszGFPhQKfMLT3iikUIQyrk\",\"is_error\":false},{\"content\":\"Successfully wrote to /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-129071/repeat_1/project_board/issues/separability_matrix_bug/testing_ticket.md\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_sPShtYiLsMQnOhVBn2G4X13d\",\"is_error\":false}]},\"inner_messages\":[{\"id\":\"d77fbf46-8cb3-48d9-a374-e12f425ece6f\",\"source\":\"ProjectManager\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":1541,\"completion_tokens\":666},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-05T16:22:54.767058Z\",\"content\":[{\"id\":\"call_gKd7632M0iFizS7XmqwCwIWy\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"issues/separability_matrix_bug/diagnosis_ticket.md\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"## Diagnosis Ticket for Separability Matrix Bug\\\\n\\\\n### Description\\\\nModeling's `separability_matrix` does not compute separability correctly for nested CompoundModels.\\\\n\\\\n### Steps to Reproduce\\\\n1. Create compound models using Astropy's modeling framework.\\\\n2. Compute separability matrix for simple and complex nested models.\\\\n3. Observe the unexpected behavior in the output of the separability m